[0.096, "o", "(209/217) installing linux-firmware-realtek                                      [##############################################] 100%\r\r\n(210/217) installing linux-firmware                                              [----------------------------------------------]   0%\r(210/217) installing linux-firmware                                              [##############################################] 100%\r\r\nOptional dependencies for linux-firmware\r\n\u001b[0;1m   \u001b[0m linux-firmware-liquidio: Firmware for Cavium LiquidIO server adapters\r\n    linux-firmware-marvell: Firmware for Marvell devices\r\n    linux-firmware-mellanox: Firmware for Mellanox Spectrum switches\r\n    linux-firmware-nfp: Firmware for Netronome Flow Processors\r\n    linux-firmware-qcom: Firmware for Qualcomm SoCs\r\n    linux-firmware-qlogic: Firmware for QLogic devices\r\n(211/217) installing python-dbus                                                 [----------------------------------------------]   0%\r(211/217) installing python-dbus                                                 [##############################################] 100%\r\r\nOptional dependencies for python-dbus\r\n\u001b[0;1m   \u001b[0m python-gobject: D-Bus services via PyGI [pending]\r\n(212/217) installing libgirepository                                             [----------------------------------------------]   0%\r(212/217) installing libgirepository                                             [##############################################] 100%\r\r\n(213/217) installing gobject-introspection-runtime                               [----------------------------------------------]   0%\r"]
